OL,3,CClaudia Winkleman quits chat show
OL,4,Cafter one series due to nerves
OL,6,FClaudia Winkleman has said she was
OL,7,F"too nervous to enjoy" her eponymous
OL,8,Ftalk show and will not bring it back
OL,9,Ffor another series.
OL,11,FThe Claudia Winkleman Show, which
OL,12,Flaunched earlier this year, saw her
OL,13,Finterview celebrity guests in front of
OL,14,Fa studio audience.
OL,16,FIn a statement, she said: "I'm
OL,17,Fincredibly grateful to the BBC for
OL,18,Fgiving me the opportunity, to the
OL,19,Fguests who agreed to come and chat to
OL,20,Fme, and the production team who were
OL,21,Fsimply excellent.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@VO]xD@[OU
