CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784251084
OL,3,CClaudia Winkleman quits chat show
OL,4,Cafter one series due to nerves
OL,6,F"Sometimes you have to try something
OL,7,Fto see how it fits, and I realised I
OL,8,Fwas just too nervous to enjoy it.
OL,10,F"Maybe one day I will give it another
OL,11,Ftry, but for now I already have the
OL,12,Fbest jobs in the world and absolutely
OL,13,Flove the shows I'm doing."
OL,15,FWinkleman, who stepped down from
OL,16,Fpresenting Strictly Come Dancing after
OL,17,F15 years last December, presents The
OL,18,FTraitors and spin-off The Celebrity
OL,19,FTraitors, as well as other TV shows.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@ZO]
