OL,3,CClaudia Winkleman quits chat show
OL,4,Cafter one series due to nerves
OL,6,FHer chat show was produced by So
OL,7,FTelevision, the company behind the
OL,8,Faward-winning The Graham Norton Show.
OL,10,FWinkleman's show filled the same
OL,11,FFriday nighttime slot on BBC One in
OL,12,Fthe gap between series, after Norton
OL,13,Freduced the number of shows he filmed
OL,14,Feach year.
OL,16,FShe interviewed guests including
OL,17,FJennifer Saunders, Dan Levy and Jeff
OL,18,FGoldblum.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
