OL,3,CClaudia Winkleman quits chat show
OL,4,Cafter one series due to nerves
OL,6,FHer show attracted an audience of
OL,7,Fbetween 1.5 million and 2 million
OL,8,Fviews, according to the BBC, with
OL,9,Fclips from chat shows attracting
OL,10,Ffurther views across social media.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FEd Havard, director of entertainment
OL,18,Fat the BBC, said: "Claudia's warmth
OL,19,Fand quick wit made The Claudia
OL,20,FWinkleman Show an absolute joy.
OL,26,@zD@SOU
