OL,3,CClaudia Winkleman quits chat show
OL,4,Cafter one series due to nerves
OL,6,F"Whilst we loved the show, we fully
OL,7,Frespect her decision and would like to
OL,8,Fthank Claudia and the brilliant team
OL,9,Fat So Television for bringing the
OL,10,Fseries to screen on the BBC.
OL,12,F"As the host of the country's most-
OL,13,Fwatched show, Claudia will be back on
OL,14,Fthe BBC very soon when The Celebrity
OL,15,FTraitors returns later this year, and
OL,16,Fwe can't wait to see what she has in
